,"position":3},"title":"Ikramah on Yusuf: Allah raised up Joseph by his forgiveness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: \u2018Ikramah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said to Joseph: O Joseph, by your forgiveness of your brothers I have raised your status among those who are mentioned.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 4471 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0646\u0639\u064a\u0645 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u0643\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u062a\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0644\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064f\u0641\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32487,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/ummah-only-supported-ikhlaas\/","url_meta":{"origin":37412,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Welfare: Muslims supported because of their weak","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah only supports this nation due to the supplications, the prayers, and the sincerity of their vulnerable.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 3178 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0648\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0635\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\